Package sicret.categories

The package contains implementations of IDecisionCategory categories for SicretRules decision tree.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CategoryCorrosive Assigned when compound is estimated to be corrosive to skin.
CategoryIrritating Assigned when compound is estimated to be irritating to skin.
CategoryIrritatingOrCorrosive Assigned when compound is estimated to be irritating or corrosive to skin.
CategoryNotCorrosive Assigned when compound is estimated to be not corrosive to skin.
CategoryNotIrritating Assigned when compound is estimated to be not irritating to skin.
CategoryNotIrritatingOrCorrosive Assigned when compound is estimated to be not Irritating or corrosive to skin.
CategoryUnknown Assigned when SicretRules are not able to estimate skin irritation or corrosive potential.
 

Package sicret.categories Description

The package contains implementations of IDecisionCategory categories for SicretRules decision tree.
